#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn48.19:0.2"
msgid "2. Mudutaravagga "
msgstr "2. Weaker "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 19. Sampannasutta → upasanno (pts1)
msgctxt "sn48.19:0.3"
msgid "19. Sampannasutta "
msgstr "19. Endowed "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn48.19:1.1"
msgid "Atha kho aññataro bhikkhu yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho so bhikkhu bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then a mendicant went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, and said to him: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.203, sc2
msgctxt "sn48.19:2.1"
msgid "“‘Indriyasampanno, indriyasampanno’ti, bhante, vuccati. "
msgstr "“Sir, they speak of someone who is ‘accomplished regarding the faculties’. "

msgctxt "sn48.19:2.2"
msgid "Kittāvatā nu kho, bhante, indriyasampanno hotī”ti? "
msgstr "How is someone accomplished regarding the faculties defined?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn48.19:2.3"
msgid "“Idha, bhikkhu, bhikkhu saddhindriyaṃ bhāveti upasamagāmiṃ sambodhagāmiṃ, vīriyindriyaṃ bhāveti upasamagāmiṃ sambodhagāmiṃ, satindriyaṃ bhāveti upasamagāmiṃ sambodhagāmiṃ, samādhindriyaṃ bhāveti upasamagāmiṃ sambodhagāmiṃ, paññindriyaṃ bhāveti upasamagāmiṃ sambodhagāmiṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicant, it’s when a mendicant develops the faculties of faith, energy, mindfulness, immersion, and wisdom that lead to peace and awakening. "

msgctxt "sn48.19:2.4"
msgid "Ettāvatā kho, bhikkhu, bhikkhu indriyasampanno hotī”ti. "
msgstr "This is how someone who is accomplished regarding the faculties is defined.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn48.19:2.5"
msgid "Navamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

